{
  "stem": "6258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were also moments of happiness, for example, when my brother came back from the POW camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When, after every terrible, well, transportation, or action, or selection, we found ourselves together and with friends and with [? tears ?] and with [? sad. ?] Well, this was that moment of, of happiness.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One, I was very happy one day when, when our dog came, just came through everything, like Lassie, come home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, but I had to-- we had to take him back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was also a kind of a happiness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, it was a different-- happiness is a very wide word.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's different.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Happiness was every nice day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Happiness, it  was we were having a flower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we were having two flowers on the window growing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But first of all, it was more unhappiness than happiness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were holidays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that orphanage, which, as a matter of fact, it was also in the building where before the war was Catholic Orphanage of Mercy-- of Catholic, well, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- people were praying there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- people were praying so fervently.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember that we were lighting candles on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because nobody had, well, candles also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I remember how people were-- everybody was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nevertheless, people were telling one another, 'Happy New Year,' and maybe everything will change, this was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look, having an older brother and house full of boys all the time, since I remember, my relation to boys and to men, generally, was somewhat different.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- I was used to fight with them or to, to-- you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not such a big deal as with many other girls who were like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
